OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChris Mason appointed new  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBBC political editor       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Chris Mason has been appointed the     
OL,6, BBC's new political editor, the        
OL,7, corporation has announced.             
OL,9,FThe Yorkshire-born broadcaster, 41, has
OL,10,Fworked as a BBC journalist for two     
OL,11,Fdecades and currently hosts Radio 4's  
OL,12,FAny Questions? programme.              
OL,14,FMason replaces Laura Kuenssberg, who   
OL,15,Fstepped down earlier this year.        
OL,17,F"What a tremendous privilege to take on
OL,18,Fwhat, for me, is the most extraordinary
OL,19,Fjob in British broadcasting and        
OL,20,Fjournalism," Mason said.               
